---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/private-calc.css';
---
<Layout title="IRPFm 2026 · Calculadoras · Invest Analysis" footerCrumb="Calculadoras">

  <style is:global>
  /* ── Seção recolhível ──────────────────────────────────────── */
  .ac-section.is-collapsible { padding: 0; }
  .ac-section.is-collapsible > .ac-section-toggle {
    width: 100%;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    padding: 26px 36px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 14px;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: inherit;
    color: inherit;
  }
  .ac-section.is-collapsible > .ac-section-toggle .ac-section-head {
    margin: 0;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    text-align: left;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .ac-section.is-collapsible > .ac-section-toggle .ac-section-head h2 {
    font-size: 19px;
  }
  .ac-section.is-collapsible > .ac-section-toggle .ac-step-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 26px; height: 26px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(0,113,227,0.10);
    color: var(--private-blue);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    margin-right: 4px;
  }
  .ac-section.is-collapsible > .ac-section-toggle .ac-section-chevron {
    width: 18px; height: 18px;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    transition: transform .22s var(--private-ease);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .ac-section.is-collapsible[data-collapsed="true"] > .ac-section-toggle .ac-section-chevron {
    transform: rotate(-90deg);
  }
  .ac-section.is-collapsible > .ac-section-body {
    padding: 0 36px 30px;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
    padding-top: 24px;
  }
  .ac-section.is-collapsible[data-collapsed="true"] > .ac-section-body {
    display: none;
  }
  .ac-section.is-collapsible > .ac-section-toggle:hover .ac-section-head h2 {
    color: var(--private-blue);
  }

  /* ── Mini summary (renderiza dentro do toggle quando fechado) ── */
  .ac-section-summary {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: right;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    max-width: 280px;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }
  .ac-section-summary strong {
    color: var(--private-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .ac-section.is-collapsible > .ac-section-toggle { padding: 22px 22px; gap: 10px; }
    .ac-section.is-collapsible > .ac-section-body { padding: 20px 22px 22px; }
    .ac-section-summary { display: none; }
  }

  /* ── Picker de quantidade de empresas ─────────────────────── */
  .div-empresas-picker {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    background: #FBFBFD;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .div-empresas-picker label {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--private-text);
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 220px;
  }
  .div-empresas-picker select {
    appearance: none;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
    background: #fff;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--private-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 9px 36px 9px 14px;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--private-text);
    cursor: pointer;
    outline: none;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 12 12' fill='none' stroke='%23636366' stroke-width='1.6' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'><polyline points='3 5 6 8 9 5'/></svg>");
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: right 12px center;
    background-size: 10px 10px;
    transition: border-color .15s var(--private-ease);
  }
  .div-empresas-picker select:focus {
    border-color: var(--private-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0,113,227,0.10);
  }
  .div-empresas-empty {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 28px 22px;
    background: var(--private-bg);
    border: 0.5px dashed var(--private-divider);
    border-radius: 14px;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .div-empresas-empty.is-on { display: flex; }
  .div-empresas-empty svg { color: var(--private-muted2); margin-bottom: 4px; }

  .div-tbl-wrap.is-hidden,
  .div-kpi-strip.is-hidden { display: none; }

  /* ── Tabela de dividendos mensais (compacta) ───────────────── */
  .div-tbl-wrap {
    overflow-x: auto;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
    background: #FBFBFD;
  }
  .div-tbl {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: separate;
    border-spacing: 0;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    min-width: 940px;
  }
  .div-tbl thead th {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 10px 6px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
    background: #FBFBFD;
    text-align: center;
    white-space: nowrap;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
  }
  .div-tbl thead th:first-child {
    text-align: left;
    padding-left: 14px;
    min-width: 140px;
  }
  .div-tbl thead th.is-total,
  .div-tbl thead th.is-irrf {
    color: var(--private-blue);
  }
  .div-tbl tbody td {
    padding: 4px 4px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
  }
  .div-tbl tbody td:first-child { padding-left: 10px; }
  .div-tbl tbody td input {
    width: 100%;
    background: transparent;
    border: 0.5px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 7px 6px;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--private-text);
    text-align: right;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    outline: none;
    transition: all .15s var(--private-ease);
  }
  .div-tbl tbody td input.div-emp {
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--private-text);
  }
  .div-tbl tbody td input:focus {
    background: #fff;
    border-color: var(--private-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(0,113,227,0.10);
  }
  .div-tbl tbody td input::placeholder {
    color: var(--private-muted2);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .div-tbl tbody td.is-calc {
    text-align: right;
    padding-right: 12px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-text);
  }
  .div-tbl tbody td.is-irrf {
    color: var(--private-blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .div-tbl tbody tr.is-total td {
    background: rgba(0,113,227,0.04);
    border-top: 0.5px solid rgba(0,113,227,0.15);
    border-bottom: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-text);
  }
  .div-tbl tbody tr.is-total td:first-child {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .div-tbl tbody tr.is-total td.is-calc { padding: 12px 12px; font-size: 13px; }

  /* ── KPI strip (Dividendos – painel de indicadores) ─────── */
  .div-kpi-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 18px;
  }
  .div-kpi {
    background: #FBFBFD;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .div-kpi .lbl {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .div-kpi .val {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-text);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    letter-spacing: -0.012em;
  }
  .div-kpi .val.blu { color: var(--private-blue); }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .div-kpi-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }

  /* ── Tabela com 4 colunas: descrição / valor / limite / aceito ── */
  .ac-row-table {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.8fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6px 12px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }
  .ac-row-table > .hdr {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 4px 4px 8px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .ac-row-table > .hdr.is-right { text-align: right; }
  .ac-row-table > .lbl {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--private-text);
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 6px 0;
  }
  .ac-row-table > .cell {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 4px 0;
  }
  .ac-row-table > .cell-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    padding: 4px 4px;
    text-align: right;
  }
  .ac-row-table > .cell-val {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-text);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    padding: 4px 4px;
  }
  .ac-row-table > .cell-val.blu { color: var(--private-blue); }
  .ac-row-table > .cell input[type="text"] {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 9px 12px;
    background: #F5F5F7;
    border: 0.5px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--private-text);
    text-align: right;
    outline: none;
    transition: all .15s var(--private-ease);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  .ac-row-table > .cell input[type="text"]:focus {
    background: #fff;
    border-color: var(--private-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0,113,227,0.10);
  }
  .ac-row-table > .group-title {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    margin-top: 14px;
    padding: 6px 0 4px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
  }
  .ac-row-table > .group-title:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .ac-row-table > .row-sep {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    border-top: 0.5px dashed var(--private-divider);
    margin: 2px 0;
  }
  .ac-row-table > .subtotal {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.8fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6px 12px;
    align-items: center;
    background: rgba(0,113,227,0.04);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .ac-row-table > .subtotal > .lbl {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-text);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .ac-row-table > .subtotal > .cell-val {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--private-blue);
    padding: 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .ac-row-table { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4px; }
    .ac-row-table > .hdr { display: none; }
    .ac-row-table > .lbl {
      font-size: 12.5px;
      padding: 8px 0 2px;
      color: var(--private-muted);
      font-weight: 500;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      font-size: 11px;
    }
    .ac-row-table > .cell { padding: 0 0 6px; }
    .ac-row-table > .cell-info { justify-content: flex-start; padding: 0 0 4px; font-size: 11px; }
    .ac-row-table > .cell-val { justify-content: flex-start; padding: 0 0 8px; }
    .ac-row-table > .subtotal {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 4px;
    }
    .ac-row-table > .row-sep { margin: 4px 0; }
  }

  /* ── Tabela progressiva 2026 ───────────────────────────── */
  .ac-table-progressive {
    margin-top: 8px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
  }
  .ac-table-progressive table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .ac-table-progressive th, .ac-table-progressive td {
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    text-align: right;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
  }
  .ac-table-progressive th {
    background: #FBFBFD;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    font-size: 10.5px;
  }
  .ac-table-progressive th:first-child,
  .ac-table-progressive td:first-child { text-align: left; }
  .ac-table-progressive tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .ac-table-progressive tr.is-active td { background: rgba(0,113,227,0.06); color: var(--private-blue); font-weight: 600; }

  /* ── Resultado final (cards) ──────────────────────────── */
  .ac-final-result {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .ac-final-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--private-border);
    box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.03), 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    padding: 22px 22px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .ac-final-card .lbl {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .ac-final-card .val {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-text);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    letter-spacing: -0.022em;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }
  .ac-final-card .sub {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .ac-final-card.is-pay {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(196,43,28,0.05) 0%, #fff 60%);
    border-color: rgba(196,43,28,0.20);
  }
  .ac-final-card.is-pay .val { color: #C42B1C; }
  .ac-final-card.is-ref {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,158,92,0.05) 0%, #fff 60%);
    border-color: rgba(0,158,92,0.22);
  }
  .ac-final-card.is-ref .val { color: #009E5C; }
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .ac-final-result { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ac-final-card .val { font-size: 26px; }
  }

  /* ── Legend (Instruções) ───────────────────────────────── */
  .ac-legend {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 10px 18px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .ac-legend > div {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--private-text);
  }
  .ac-legend .dot {
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border: 0.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .ac-legend .desc { color: var(--private-muted); font-size: 12.5px; }
  .ac-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .ac-step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: center;
    background: #FBFBFD;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--private-text);
  }
  .ac-step .n {
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--private-blue);
    color: #fff;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .ac-legend { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* ── Diagnostico (badge final) ─────────────────────────── */
  .ac-diag {
    margin-top: 14px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: #FBFBFD;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--private-divider);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--private-text);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .ac-diag .ttl {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .ac-diag strong { font-weight: 600; }

  /* ── Tip discreta ──────────────────────────────────────── */
  .ac-section-tip {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--private-muted);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .ac-section-tip strong { color: var(--private-text); font-weight: 600; }
  </style>

  <div slot="topbar-sub" class="atb-sub">
    <div class="atb-sub-pages">
      <a href="/calculadoras/simular-pgbl.html"  class="atb-sub-page">PGBL</a>
      <a href="/calculadoras/aposentadoria.html" class="atb-sub-page">Aposentadoria</a>
      <a href="/calculadoras/irpfm.html"         class="atb-sub-page is-active">IRPFm 2026</a>
      <a href="/calculadoras/sucessao-previdencia.html" class="atb-sub-page">Sucessão na Previdência</a>
    </div>
    <div class="atb-kpis" aria-live="polite"><div class="atb-kpi-group is-active" data-kpi="cdi"><span class="atb-kpi-group-label">CDI</span><div class="atb-kpi"><span class="atb-kpi-label" data-month>—</span><span class="atb-kpi-value" data-kpi-val="mes">—</span></div><div class="atb-kpi is-secondary"><span class="atb-kpi-label">Ano</span><span class="atb-kpi-value" data-kpi-val="ano">—</span></div><div class="atb-kpi is-tertiary"><span class="atb-kpi-label">12m</span><span class="atb-kpi-value" data-kpi-val="12m">—</span></div></div><div class="atb-kpi-group" data-kpi="ibov"><span class="atb-kpi-group-label">Ibov</span><div class="atb-kpi"><span class="atb-kpi-label" data-month>—</span><span class="atb-kpi-value" data-kpi-val="mes">—</span></div><div class="atb-kpi is-secondary"><span class="atb-kpi-label">Ano</span><span class="atb-kpi-value" data-kpi-val="ano">—</span></div><div class="atb-kpi is-tertiary"><span class="atb-kpi-label">12m</span><span class="atb-kpi-value" data-kpi-val="12m">—</span></div></div></div>
  </div>


<section class="page-hero" data-private-hero>
  <p class="eyebrow">Calculadoras · IRPFm 2026</p>
  <h1>Imposto de Renda Mínimo. <span class="muted">Quanto vai pagar?</span></h1>
  <p>Apuração completa do IRPFm sobre dividendos, salário e demais rendimentos. Parâmetros: Lei 15.270/2025 (ano-calendário 2026, DAA 2027).</p>
</section>

<div class="ac-page ac-page-wide">

  <div class="ac-warn-big" role="note" aria-label="Aviso legal">
    <svg class="ac-warn-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/>
      <line x1="12" y1="9"  x2="12" y2="13"/>
      <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/>
    </svg>
    <div>
      <p class="ac-warn-title">Atenção — interpretação técnica da Lei 15.270/2025</p>
      <p class="ac-warn-body">
        O <strong>IRPFm</strong> ainda passará por regulamentação infralegal da Receita Federal e poderá ter pontos esclarecidos por instrução normativa, solução de consulta ou jurisprudência. Todos os números desta página são <strong>simulações</strong> calculadas a partir da <strong>interpretação atual</strong> da lei. Outras interpretações são possíveis e o entendimento oficial pode divergir. Antes de qualquer decisão tributária, especialmente na DAA 2027, <strong>valide os valores com seu contador</strong> ou advogado tributarista de confiança. Esta calculadora não constitui aconselhamento fiscal.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ac-toolbar">
    <nav class="ac-breadcrumb" aria-label="Navegação">
      <a href="/index.html">Início</a>
      <span class="ac-breadcrumb-sep">›</span>
      <span class="ac-breadcrumb-current">Calculadoras</span>
      <span class="ac-breadcrumb-sep">›</span>
      <span class="ac-breadcrumb-current">IRPFm 2026</span>
    </nav>
